More refactorings (#27)

* Unrawify docstrings

* Upgrade syntax to python3.6+

* Remove leading underscore from util functions

* Configure isort interoperability with black

* Rewrite loop in normalize_words

* Remove unused main invocation in test_conversions

* Make variable names more descriptive

* Introduce for-else loop in advanced_acronym_detection

* Pythonize if

* Rename variable was_upper to was_all_upper to better reflect its purpose

* Update docstrings of all conversion functions

* Update docstring of parse_case

* Remove aliasing

* Declassify conversion methods

* Move parse_case into its own file

* Mirror test and src dir structure

* Work on types

* Use splat to simplify conversion functions

* Update docstrings of convenience functions

* Update docstrings in utils

* Restrict flake8 to src
